dct_description_sm: Sté. d'Éditions Cartographiques, 25, Av. du Maine, Paris XVe.

Shows woods (by coloring), variously sized towns, regional names, various boundaries, waterways, various rail lines, various roads and paths (including those for bicycles and with a grade higher than 5%).
Sugny town and region on Belgium and France border has boundaries on all sides.
